The difference between individual intra-module node degree and average intra-module node degree is variance-normalized to produce a z-score which allows the assignment of connector hubs at zi > 2.5 (zi > 1 in functional connectivity networks)29,30. The participation coefficient is calculated as:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
